# Architecture

The authoritative architecture and module status document lives in `docs/architecture_implementation_plan.mdc`.
Always consult that file for the package layout, dependency list, module status, and test coverage matrix.

Quick data flow reminder (see architecture doc for full details):

- `run` → load GnuCash → filter candidates → index emails → OCR receipts → match → predict → save proposals
- `review` → Flask web app → one-by-one approval with evidence checkboxes → persist decisions
- `apply` → load decisions → backup → write XML (descriptions + split accounts) → audit + journal
